# Add these DNS records at your domain registrar (A records → droplet public IPv4).
#
# Type  Name   Value
# A     @      <DROPLET_IP>
# A     www    <DROPLET_IP>
# A     wiki   <DROPLET_IP>
# A     book   <DROPLET_IP>
#
# After propagation, run: CERTBOT_EMAIL=you@example.com sudo infra/scripts/setup-ssl.sh
